<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kalvari-a zawhna lopi,
 Angel in Amah chawian ding,
 Mipite'n le chawian unau,
 Khawvel Hukdampa thisan in;
 Mi mangthai ding tat in a um,
 Kidote kichamna ahi.

[V2]
 2. Tang dang cheng sangin Kalvari,
 A minthang in a lopi zaw'i;
 Zie chun hinna tuinak a put,
 Leisiet gam chengah a luong viel;
 Namtin mihiem hin kitna di'n,
 Kumsawta hinna tui hi'na.</lyrics>
<title>LANGOEDMOR</title>
<hymn_number>96</hymn_number>
</song>